## English

Tic Tactic Toe is a strategic evolution of the classic Tic Tac Toe — designed for players who want more than just Xs and Os. This tactical board game blends logic, turn-based gameplay, and deep analysis to deliver a smarter experience.

🧠 Play against a smart bot:
• 3 difficulty levels: from random moves to Minimax AI  
• Blocking, forks, win-line detection

🎮 Play with a friend:
• Local multiplayer on one device  
• Adaptive gameplay with tournament-style rounds

🧩 Game setup:
• Grid sizes from 8×8 to 12×12  
• Win condition: 3 to 6 in a row  
• Turn timer: 7 to 60 seconds  
• Choose player colors, names, and game mode

🌐 Localization:
• Supports 11 languages: English, Русский, Українська, Español, Deutsch, Português, हिन्दी, Bahasa Indonesia, 中文, 日本語, 한국어

📊 Game analysis:
• Highlights winning line with glow effects  
• Shows move numbers  
• Tracks time, missed turns, and stats

🎨 Design:
• Light blue UI  
• Glow visuals  
• Minimalist style

📤 Feedback:
• Email: vonnab.e.v@gmail.com

📱 Offline play:
• No internet required

⚙️ Built with Flutter:
• Cross-platform  
• Optimized for Android 8+

If you're looking for a Tic Tac Toe that actually makes you think — Tic Tactic Toe is built for you.

